Class Project

  • java.lang.Object
    • Project

  • public class Project
extends java.lang.Object
    This method is used as a user defined object called Project.

    Fields for this object includes, project number, project name, building type, physical address, ERF Number, total fee, total paid, project deadline, project status, project completion date, project architect, project contractor and project customer.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Nadia Botha
